room_title: Escape room "Hostel Dread" by Premier Escape Rooms in San Antonio
room_address: 19186 Blanco Rd Ste 102 San Antonio, TX 78258
room_description: One of your friends has been missing for a few days and you haven't been able to contact them. You and a few other friends decide to go looking for them in the hostel they had been staying at. When you get there the fear starts to build in your group after seeing the grim looking scene of the room. But everyone decides to start looking for any clues to find your friend. You better find out where your friend is and get out before time runs out or you could end up missing as well...
